Title: Log In with valid username/password
Precondition: User is on Log In page
Steps:
1. Open Log In popup
2. Enter valid username & password
3. Click "Login"
Expected Result: User successfully logged in → Navbar shows "Welcome username"

Title: Log In with valid username + wrong password
Steps:
1. Open Log In popup
2. Enter valid username & wrong password
3. Click "Login"

Title: Log In with non-existing username
Steps:
1. Open Log In popup
2. Enter non-existing username & any password
3. Click "Login"

Title: Log In with empty fields
Steps:
1. Open Log In popup
2. Leave username & password empty
3. Click" Login"
Expected Result: Alert: "Please fill out Username and Password"
Actual Result: Alert shows "Please fill out Username and Password"

Title: Both username and password invalid
Steps:
1. Enter wrong username
2. Enter wrong password
3. Click on “Login"

Title: Username field empty, password filled
Steps:
1. Leave username empty
2. Enter password
3. Click on “Login"
Expected Result: Alert: "Please fill out Username and Password"

Title: Password field empty, username filled
Steps:
1. Enter username
2. Leave password empty
3. Click on “Login"
Expected Result: Alert: "Please fill out Username and Password"
